Title: The Voyeur's Web
Plot: The NCIS team takes upon a strange case - a Marine's wife was murdered live on the Internet. The investigation reveals that two housewives were running a live Internet sex site and now they are both missing. While looking for them, the team will try to track down the webmaster and solve the alleged murder case.
GuestStars: Bradley White, Brian Dietzen, Michael Bellisario, Nat Faxon, John Eric Bentley, Martin Papazian, Brittney Powell, Lauren Holly
